data.description: VRM, the Seller will entertain offers between $389,000 and $420,000.  Discover the epitome of Southern living in this meticulously designed 5-bedroom, 3-full bath brick home located in the heart of Saraland, Alabama. With timeless curb appeal and a well-maintained lawn, this classic brick home leads to an inviting interior featuring an open-concept layout, hardwood flooring, and an abundance of natural light. The kitchen, a culinary haven with modern appliances and a large central island, seamlessly connects to the breakfast area and living room, creating an ideal space for entertaining. The spacious living room has a cozy fireplace and offers versatility as well. The primary suite, a true owners retreat, boasts a luxurious en-suite bathroom and a expansive walk-in closet, while the additional bedrooms provide ample space. Outside, a two-car garage and a fenced backyard with a covered back porch offer both convenience and privacy, making it a perfect setting for outdoor activities and gatherings. Living in Saraland, Alabama, brings the added charm of a close-knit community, excellent schools, and easy access to major highways, ensuring a perfect balance of comfort and convenience. Don't miss the chance to call this Saraland residence your home, where Southern hospitality meets modern elegance. Schedule your showing today and envision a life of warmth and joy in this exceptional property.  All updates per the Seller. LISTING BROKER MAKES NO REPRESENTATION TO SQUARE FOOTAGE ACCURACY.
